{"tid":1136414,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"［真心一問］點樣有大陸香港兩個號碼，而唔使出賣哂私隱","createTime":"2019-05-03T03:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T05:57:51.000Z","uid":87328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"31c5036f06b32b9c39fefea28639422f82558b23","tid":1136414,"uid":87328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"因為工作原因，香港大陸兩邊跑。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下大家有咩好既電話or 電話卡方法，可以用到支付寶/大陸系統，而又唔使出賣所有個人資料俾內地政府？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家既做法就係用兩個電話，一個係垃圾紅米（大陸電話卡/實名），另外就係一路用開既iphone (香港電話卡/深水埗買既data card)。希望佢監唔到我香港個電話就算。但係攞住兩個電話又好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇過d一卡兩號plan，但係覺得唔可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家俾少少意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（雖然香港政府遲早都推埋實名...）"},{"pid":"c29f746bf8d4fb7fe77f6ff840b8013a0379b9dc","tid":1136414,"uid":237794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63640e115b7a7ecc2f7dc83cce4ac9116c311bf0","tid":1136414,"uid":245689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25099961e0247bbdab7fc6c044536019233140cd","tid":1136414,"uid":237794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e4cd4120828fef4a15abe080802867aead03501","tid":1136414,"uid":175383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7f6d5c8e048fccc5ee4eaf409866a0fdbf509d6","tid":1136414,"uid":237794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47bbcd8255a1e8f048623d42492ec696ee6afbfe","tid":1136414,"uid":171852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T